eply_to": 864072331, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775785783}, {"pid": 864075029, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 10:05", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[img]./mon_202604/10/jmQ2x-lad5K8T1kScr-1f.jpg[/img]<br/>听说你们昨天讨论宏和？[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 1942, "content_length": 57, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202604/10/jmQ2x-lad5K8T1kScr-1f.jpg", "size": 9, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202604/10", "name": "jmQ2x-lad5K8T1kScr-1f.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775786730}, {"pid": 864075372, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 10:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864075149,45974302,3611]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38090976]sora496[/uid] (2026-04-10 10:06):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大真应该给我打钱，又带他吃个板[/quote]<br/>啧啧 我这两天给你们的哪个没有大几个点  而且直接买直接有 不像小图先套你两个月", "lou": 1943, "content_length": 77, "reply_to": 864075149, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775786884}, {"pid": 864075645, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 37, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 10:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "准备4020咯  这次一卖和二卖基本预判达成<br/>我不懂你们前面怎么看  我反正按我的 4020-4030内 回退仓位。", "lou": 1944, "content_length": 89, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775786993}, {"pid": 864078572, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 13, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 10:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864078373,45974302,3616]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65204484]饿有饿报[/uid] (2026-04-10 10:28):[/b]<br/><br/>你猜狼大喊一声会不会一条直线下去[s:ac:哭笑]泥潭营业部和潜在的量化机器人可不是开玩笑的[/quote]<br/>我昨天不是说我止盈了天银么[s:ac:偷笑]", "lou": 1945, "content_length": 29, "reply_to": 864078373, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775788210}, {"pid": 864079020, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 68, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 10:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864078762,45974302,3617]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64022196]7ucky7[/uid] (2026-04-10 10:31):[/b]<br/><br/>天银机电清了是说了的，狼大先跑，我们后跑[s:ac:花痴][/quote]<br/>昨天甚至没有天银的家人给我点个赞 要给这些人点点踩才行<br/>我决定了 等跌完我才发我清了  然后还要举报说这些家人恶意做空", "lou": 1946, "content_length": 113, "reply_to": 864078762, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775788401}, {"pid": 864079079, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 10:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864078887,45974302,3617]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60099555]咪了个咕[/uid] (2026-04-10 10:32):[/b]<br/><br/>宏和真在里面，涨停被你爆头了？[/quote]<br/>你有病啊  可用余额0", "lou": 1947, "content_length": 22, "reply_to": 864078887, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775788425}, {"pid": 864080043, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 58, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 10:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们知道指数为什么不跌吗<br/>看看+8的同花顺<br/>这就是典型的机构操盘方法了 我之前分享过多次[s:ac:哭笑]<br/>现在是我的舒适区", "lou": 1948, "content_length": 94, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775788814}, {"pid": 864080405, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 59, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 10:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我教你们个方法  卖出去的怕忍不住买回来怎么  所有自己手上的票找低位的线挂进去 不管是黄金分割 还是均线  挂远一点<br/>然后看盘也行 聊天也行  分散注意力。", "lou": 1949, "content_length": 134, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775788961}, {"pid": 864080472, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 30, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 10:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864080327,45974302,3618]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66983776]大时代冲冲冲[/uid] (2026-04-10 10:42):[/b]<br/><br/>坚定等4020[/quote]<br/>我不差那10个指数点[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 1950, "content_length": 21, "reply_to": 864080327, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775788990}, {"pid": 864084024, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 11:07", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864083518,45974302,3623]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60621194]HoshiZorA_Z[/uid] (2026-04-10 11:03):[/b]<br/><br/>指数感觉已经有点兜不住了，等散户反应过来，应该会砸的更快[s:ac:哭笑]<br/>但英子还是好猛，我还以为他要在80磨一磨[/quote]<br/>个股有个股的逻辑  反正这段时间 低位就是好  高位就是不好  这对应大部分的票<br/>但是指数也没有很差  这里都是诱多后的避让而已 不代表8000E增量现在会大跑路", "lou": 1951, "content_length": 140, "reply_to": 864083518, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775790442}, {"pid": 864084140, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 46, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 11:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "反正对于YWK我的看法没变过 3季度验货", "lou": 1952, "content_length": 34, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775790489}, {"pid": 864085018, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 11:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864084688,45974302,3625]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38700657]流星桐[/uid] (2026-04-10 11:11):[/b]<br/><br/>说实话，我基本每天都看着，ywk从100到80多这段掉下来很快，以为会在80多横盘调整一段时间，但是真没想到启动那么快的....[/quote]<br/>这哪有启动  不过就是超跌后的反弹  还是最后才反的  已经落后其他液冷了", "lou": 1953, "content_length": 67, "reply_to": 864084688, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775790825}, {"pid": 864085219, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 11:15", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864084539,45974302,3624]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=43014880]海棠花未眠之梦[/uid] (2026-04-10 11:10):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大昨天按纪律上轨减了铁盒，今天知道自己没做日内t能力直接没买等回踩，算不算守纪律的中庸操作[s:ac:喘][/quote]<br/>我按纪律可能挣不到最多  但是一定亏少挣多 我只是想安稳过去", "lou": 1954, "content_length": 59, "reply_to": 864084539, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775790912}, {"pid": 864085871, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 14, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 11:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864085295,45974302,3625]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60621194]HoshiZorA_Z[/uid] (2026-04-10 11:15):[/b]<br/><br/>这波反弹结束应该会下去找底了吧，从3794那个低点来看，最近指数的底一直是接近45度斜线向上<br/>画了下线差不多刚好就在缺口上方，感觉这个跳空缺有可能作为C的底，起码也是个强支撑位<br/>记得之前火机哥也说过，这个位置走B的话时间上算应该差不多了，如果下去回踩缺口之后走C，那就看这个缺口上方的支撑怎么样？<br/>毕竟，这个缺是实打实8000e放量买出来的[/quote]<br/>出顶才能算回踩位 现在哪里算得出来 我又不是神仙", "lou": 1955, "content_length": 49, "reply_to": 864085295, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775791172}, {"pid": 864087508, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 11:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "半导体材料类 鼎龙和新阳已经做完成本  还剩一个没做出来  可惜了<br/>这一波也可以了", "lou": 1956, "content_length": 70, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775791845}, {"pid": 864087722, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 51, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 11:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864087366,45974302,3628]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=9438500]aot10086[/uid] (2026-04-10 11:29):[/b]<br/><br/>只能说大佬们把散户心态点的太准了，要不是跟楼早些时候我就是这样的。[/quote]<br/>前面大家都说要跌的时候 只有我敢直接放话  一卖3955 二卖4020  <br/>你们回忆一下当时的恐慌情绪 最轻的都是看踩第二只脚。严重一点的就是直接牛转熊了", "lou": 1957, "content_length": 135, "reply_to": 864087366, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775791931}, {"pid": 864091411, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 30, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 12:00", "subj